rmed the bulk of their stars at z>5 and these\nobjects probably undergo at least two periods of AGN activity: one at high\nredshift during which the black hole forms and another one at an epoch\ncorresponding to z~1.5.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Nov 2000 13:58:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-24"}
