en widely used. The calculated magnetization curves are in a good agreement\nwith experimental data on high-T$_c$ superconductors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Nov 2000 10:46:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 20 Jan 2001 09:33:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-31"}
